{"tid":684393,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"做左一年個人稅 （香港、美國） 稅務問題有問必答","createTime":"2018-05-30T13:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T07:48:56.000Z","uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6da05c02faacb02b3734772151449e414716a10a","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:22:35.000Z","msg":"剩係識Individual tax...<br />\n<br />\n香港：Salaries Tax, Property Tax, Profits tax (sole-pro), Personal Assessment<br />\n美國：1040/1040NR/states<br />\n<br />\n見好多人都認識個人稅務責任<br />\n又唔識稅務管理<br />\n<br />\n所以我認識都會答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  容許既幫你計埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：廢柴 唔係CPA member <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45d33bc596e8727f878784ad1745847e93dbe36","tid":684393,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7fd20070276bb033f35c91983d595d910f7ebdf","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e45d33bc596e8727f878784ad1745847e93dbe36","tid":684393,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8a11efab1e30f3cc13fe27a6917967f6a60208","tid":684393,"uid":26253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"係咪好多人報父母同住但事實上分開住"},{"pid":"3f57f06db35ebfba9b17ac92ec8090cdc0bc57a5","tid":684393,"uid":129309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"我做裝修想報稅，目的係做職業證明日後用黎買樓，係咪應該報入息稅？"},{"pid":"8253ba2e93649cd4f1d47a3e9d5dac9b81de7c96","tid":684393,"uid":129309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f57f06db35ebfba9b17ac92ec8090cdc0bc57a5","tid":684393,"uid":129309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"我做裝修想報稅，目的係做職業證明日後用黎買樓，係咪應該報入息稅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"因為一開始已經係自僱人士，身邊d人一係打工一係無報稅搵唔到人問"},{"pid":"76a52c0cd0e25d8cdb21f4fb5e75c6c4b5181267","tid":684393,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:40:57.000Z","msg":"信用卡回贈所得收入<br />\n洗唔洗報稅"},{"pid":"380afa4027965df33147ef1d95b64b2ac0ba475f","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c8a11efab1e30f3cc13fe27a6917967f6a60208","tid":684393,"uid":26253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"係咪好多人報父母同住但事實上分開住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"老實講係<br />\n稅局通常唔會challenge<br />\n只要唔係多過一個人claim 同一個父母（兄弟姊妹）<br />\n稅局邊得閒查你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a64548447f602c551cedc93c16c3a7fd93fbbc","tid":684393,"uid":167294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"報屋企同住扣稅會唔會影響老豆報稅？"},{"pid":"177a7ff0e7a8ba8bbb55e07d4fe21858ce9956f9","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8253ba2e93649cd4f1d47a3e9d5dac9b81de7c96","tid":684393,"uid":129309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f57f06db35ebfba9b17ac92ec8090cdc0bc57a5","tid":684393,"uid":129309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"我做裝修想報稅，目的係做職業證明日後用黎買樓，係咪應該報入息稅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"因為一開始已經係自僱人士，身邊d人一係打工一係無報稅搵唔到人問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"買樓入息申報呢層我就唔清楚（唔知需要啲咩 同你既目的係乜）<br />\n<br />\n但自僱人士應該申請商業登記，並填寫BIR60 （稅表）第五部- 利得稅<br />\n<br />\n建議簡單用個excel<br />\n填返收入減支出，將所有證明保存好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n------------------來自稅局網--------------<br />\n<br />\n如果你從買賣貨品、提供專業或個人服務賺取入息，你就會被視為經營行業、業務或專業，亦即自僱人士。<br />\n<br />\n小型業務（指總入息不超過 $2,000,000 的業務）<br />\n \t \t <br />\n \t \t<br />\n如果你的獨資業務的總入息不超過 $2,000,000，你在提交報稅表時無需夾附任何帳目和文件，否則你便須連同有關文件一併提交。<br />\n雖然你在報稅時無需為小型業務提交任何帳目和文件，但你仍須擬備帳目、並依據你擬備的帳目來填寫報稅表，以及保留所有帳目和單據，以便本局日後查詢時可提交查驗。<br />\n---------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"550e72978b60fd749e0effeaf28d9679541ad7a8","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95a64548447f602c551cedc93c16c3a7fd93fbbc","tid":684393,"uid":167294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"報屋企同住扣稅會唔會影響老豆報稅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"唔影響<br />\n反而假如你要交Salaries tax <br />\na你父母係55歲以上<br />\nb你有比家用/錢超過12,000<br />\nc父母係香港住<br />\n<br />\n每個父/母可以有23,000減免 ［2017/18］<br />\n另外全年一齊住<br />\n你可以再多23,000 減免<br />\n<br />\n如果你父母60以上，以上數字乘2"},{"pid":"551e81514245b27001ea1fb2c29547284a5d4e10","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76a52c0cd0e25d8cdb21f4fb5e75c6c4b5181267","tid":684393,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:40:57.000Z","msg":"信用卡回贈所得收入<br />\n洗唔洗報稅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"香港唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b06f7c28f8601ba1815436828b48dcec2faad2","tid":684393,"uid":32187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:39:27.000Z","msg":"點入行？big 4?"},{"pid":"0ecc075adf0a305705d75dcac4343c82aabe9e2f","tid":684393,"uid":41958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"請問如果同老豆分開住<br />\n佢有拎綜援<br />\n但我家用每個月有俾3500佢<br />\n過60歲<br />\n<br />\n有冇得減稅？"},{"pid":"4eee2a14c4ad190559c7e027bf12c08a48696db3","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b06f7c28f8601ba1815436828b48dcec2faad2","tid":684393,"uid":32187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:39:27.000Z","msg":"點入行？big 4?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"睇招聘網站 廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6972186ca11b1746374cae602dcaa76ba643eb5","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ecc075adf0a305705d75dcac4343c82aabe9e2f","tid":684393,"uid":41958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"請問如果同老豆分開住<br />\n佢有拎綜援<br />\n但我家用每個月有俾3500佢<br />\n過60歲<br />\n<br />\n有冇得減稅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"香港通常居住？ Yes"},{"pid":"6c583e7fb3960de0a65880226a8b5d8add9d2720","tid":684393,"uid":41958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6972186ca11b1746374cae602dcaa76ba643eb5","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ecc075adf0a305705d75dcac4343c82aabe9e2f","tid":684393,"uid":41958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"請問如果同老豆分開住<br />\n佢有拎綜援<br />\n但我家用每個月有俾3500佢<br />\n過60歲<br />\n<br />\n有冇得減稅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"香港通常居住？ Yes"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"香港住啊，仲以為佢有拎綜援我唔填得添，thanks!"},{"pid":"79fa6daee700c1e6484d8bf8722066efcdfcbd50","tid":684393,"uid":78700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:14:07.000Z","msg":"喺香港銀行戶口拎錢去美國買樓使唔使交稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b19857881259eb8cd0b86c451e941cbffc8cae2","tid":684393,"uid":181767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"邊間big4 幾時轉工"},{"pid":"55063bc5853b8a11e13961250627cd0d9c144bd1","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b19857881259eb8cd0b86c451e941cbffc8cae2","tid":684393,"uid":181767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"邊間big4 幾時轉工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:23:58.000Z","msg":"廢柴點會入big4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0861a6e028ec3f6db7cc7c77fae02ba97e037fb1","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79fa6daee700c1e6484d8bf8722066efcdfcbd50","tid":684393,"uid":78700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:14:07.000Z","msg":"喺香港銀行戶口拎錢去美國買樓使唔使交稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:41:27.000Z","msg":"都係睇返間樓係邊 係香港/外國銀行既錢唔關事<br />\n美國樓要諗下買樓後既責任<br />\n<br />\n最好係問左Tax advice 同埋其他專業人士先好買啊<br />\n<br />\n1. 買樓後你每年要交Property tax 即使唔出租都要繳交<br />\n會根據你係邊個州買 而有唔同Tax rate <br />\n唔同香港 出租先收tax<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果你出租係需要填寫返聯邦政府稅表（Form 1040) 同埋睇返果個州認唔認可 只填聯邦稅表 好多州都要你額外再交當地既稅 <br />\n<br />\n其次 一旦你要填美國稅表 你其他美國收入都需要申報<br />\n<br />\n3. 美國係有Capital Gain Tax 當你賣樓時你都要交稅"},{"pid":"d773fd199ed3c1deeea2d6c860a1a7c9b7f6818f","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79fa6daee700c1e6484d8bf8722066efcdfcbd50","tid":684393,"uid":78700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:14:07.000Z","msg":"喺香港銀行戶口拎錢去美國買樓使唔使交稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:44:40.000Z","msg":"你係拎去放租定自住？"},{"pid":"d455ac1e2abae07051bcd3747029e3eece930bdd","tid":684393,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92ace2f2bf4277b845306862a316c9d2351c8f7","tid":684393,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}